original_title: 羞恥！新任ナース病棟着任前強●健康診断2021秋研修医の実験台にさせられた私たち
overview: Today is the day when new nurses have their health checkups before they arrive at the ward. When I arrived at the venue, I saw a new male nurse and a male trainee who were in the same period. "Are you going to take it off in front of a man?" Feeling startled when you touch her nipples, having her urinalyzed on the spot, having her vaginal pressure checked, saying, "You're really tight, aren't you?" Please enjoy.
title: Shame! Before the Newly Appointed Nurse Takes Up a Post at the Hospital Ward, She Gets a Mandatory Medical Examination. In Autumn 2021, We Were Guinea Pigs for the Medical Interns.
